      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דאי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 38a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "גרסי' וי\"ו בכולהו",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 38a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אם כן במסקנא דמוקי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 38a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 38a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לה כרבי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 38a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 38a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לימא ר' יהודה היא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 38a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דאמר",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 38a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 38a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ולא לך",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 38a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "פרטא הוא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 38a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אבל השתא לא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 38a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מתוקמא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 38a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כוותיה דהא תרוייהו חשיב פרטא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 38a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בין בוי\"ו בין בלא וי\"ו",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 38a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ואסוגיא דשמעתין",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 38a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "קשיא דמוכח בפ\"ב דזבחים (דף ל: ושם) דטפי הוי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 38a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "פרטא בלא וי\"ו מבוי\"ו לר' יהודה דאמר התם או דלמא כזית וכזית לר' יהודה פרטא הוי וכל",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 38a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שכן כזית כזית ובספר ישן גרס הכא כולה סוגיא איפכא ור' יוחנן אמר הכל מודים",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 38a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בלא לך שהוא פרט לא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 38a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "900px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "נחלקו אלא בולא לך וגרסינן תני ולא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 38a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לך תני פקדון ותשומת יד",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 38a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כו' <big><b>כללו</b></big>. פי' לא לך פרטו של ר\"מ פי' בקונטרס דאי לרבי יהודה נמי פרט הוי אמאי נקט",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 38a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ר' יהודה טפי ולא לך וא\"ת הא דלא נקט לא לך משום דמודה בה ר\"מ וי\"ל דמכל",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 38a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מקום הוה ליה למימר אף ולא לך <big><b>הרי</b></big>. גבי שבועת",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 38a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "העדות מיתנייא דגבי פקדון הוה ליה למימר אשמות <big><b>אנסת</b></big>. תימה למאי דלא מחייבין בהזהב (ב\"מ דף",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 38a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מח.) אלא ביחוד כלי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 38a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "א\"כ הכא כיון דפרעיה תו לא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 38a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מיפטר בהודאה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 38a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "900px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "וי\"ל כגון שיחד לו בענין",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 38a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "זה שיגבה מן הכלי כל מה שיחייבוהו בית דין",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 38a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    }
  ]
}